publisher			Lumenox ehf							
publish_time	 2015年2月23日		
desc_long							评测						“Aaru’s Awakening is a phenomenal piece of art, and a solidly built game to boot”5/5 – Twinfinite“While it won’t ever hold your hand, Aaru’s Awakening will impress you with its simple mechanics, gorgeous art, and challenging (but fair) gameplay.”95/100 – VentureBeat“The journey of Aaru’s Awakening is an enchanting one. It is filled with challenging platforming and a beautiful and timeless story that is haunted by danger.”Indie Game Magazine												关于这款游戏							Aaru's Awakening is a hand-drawn, fast-paced 2D action platformer. The game puts players in charge of Aaru, a mythical creature with two unique abilities teleportation and charging. He uses these abilities as he travels through the dangerous world of Lumenox to defeat an evil entity. These two abilities are at the heart of every level design throughout the game, to make for a challenging and fluid experience. The levels require players to make split second decisions whilst completing fast-paced puzzles.						
title	 Aaru's Awakening			
